vulnerability.name: USN-5086-1
vulnerability.description: Johan Almbladh discovered that the eBPF JIT implementation for IBM s390x systems in the Linux kernel miscompiled operations in some situations, allowing circumvention of the BPF verifier. A local attacker could use this to cause a denial of service (system crash) or possibly execute arbitrary code.

statements.status_notes: IBM s390x systems could be made to crash or run programs as an administrator.
